{"id":37,"parent_id":30,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":37,"title":"2 Nephi 7","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 7"],[".studySummary",["i","Jacob continues reading from Isaiah: Isaiah speaks messianically—The Messiah will have the tongue of the learned—He will give His back to the smiters—He will not be confounded—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50"},"Isaiah 50"],". About 559–545",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.1","order":"05.13.007.3847"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Yea"],", for thus saith the Lord: Have I put thee away, or have I cast thee off forever? For thus saith the Lord: Where is the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"bill"],"of your mother’s",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"divorcement"],"? To whom have I put thee away, or to which of my",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"creditors"],"have I",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_1e"},"sold"],"you? Yea, to whom have I sold you? Behold, for your iniquities have ye sold yourselves, and for your transgressions is your mother put away."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.2","order":"05.13.007.3848"},["b","2"],"Wherefore, when I came, there was no man; when I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"called"],", yea, there was none to answer. O house of Israel, is my hand shortened at all that it cannot redeem, or have I no power to deliver? Behold, at my rebuke I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"dry up"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"sea"],", I make their",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"rivers"],"a wilderness and their",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_2e"},"fish"],"to stink because the waters are dried up, and they die because of thirst."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.3","order":"05.13.007.3849"},["b","3"],"I clothe the heavens with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"blackness"],", and I make",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"sackcloth"],"their covering."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.4","order":"05.13.007.3850"},["b","4"],"The Lord God hath given me the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"tongue"],"of the learned, that I should know how to speak a word in season unto thee, O house of Israel. When ye are weary he waketh morning by morning. He waketh mine ear to hear as the learned."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.5","order":"05.13.007.3851"},["b","5"],"The Lord God hath opened mine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"ear"],", and I was not rebellious, neither turned away back."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.6","order":"05.13.007.3852"},["b","6"],"I gave my back to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"smiter"],", and my cheeks to them that plucked off the hair. I hid not my face from",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"shame"],"and spitting."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.7","order":"05.13.007.3853"},["b","7"],"For the Lord God will help me, therefore shall I not be confounded. Therefore have I set my face like a flint, and I know that I shall not be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"ashamed"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.8","order":"05.13.007.3854"},["b","8"],"And the Lord is near, and he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"justifieth"],"me. Who will contend with me? Let us stand together. Who is mine adversary? Let him come near me, and I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"smite"],"him with the strength of my mouth."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.9","order":"05.13.007.3855"},["b","9"],"For the Lord God will help me. And all they who shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"condemn"],"me, behold, all they shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"wax old"],"as a garment, and the moth shall eat them up."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.10","order":"05.13.007.3856"},["b","10"],"Who is among you that feareth the Lord, that obeyeth the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"voice"],"of his servant, that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"walketh"],"in darkness and hath no light?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.11","order":"05.13.007.3857"},["b","11"],"Behold all ye that kindle fire, that compass yourselves about with sparks, walk in the light of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"your"],"fire and in the sparks which ye have kindled.",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"This"],"shall ye have of mine hand—ye shall lie down in sorrow."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.1a","order":"05.13.007.3858"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.1.1-11"},"Isa. 50:1 (1–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.1"},"2 Ne. 8:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.1b","order":"05.13.007.3860"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/3.8"},"Jer. 3:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.1c","order":"05.13.007.3862"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/divorce"},"TG Divorce"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.1d","order":"05.13.007.3864"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/4.1"},"2 Kgs. 4:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/18.25"},"Matt. 18:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"1e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.1e","order":"05.13.007.3866"},["b","1e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/4.2"},"Judg. 4:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/52.3"},"Isa. 52:3"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.2a","order":"05.13.007.3868"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/1.24.24-27"},"Prov. 1:24 (24–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.12"},"Isa. 65:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.37"},"Alma 5:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.2b","order":"05.13.007.3870"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.4"},"Nahum 1:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.2c","order":"05.13.007.3872"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/14.21.1-31"},"Ex. 14:21 (1–31)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.9"},"Ps. 106:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.68"},"D&C 133:68"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.2d","order":"05.13.007.3874"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/3.16.15-16"},"Josh. 3:16 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.2e","order":"05.13.007.3876"},["b","2e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/7.21.17-21"},"Ex. 7:21 (17–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.3a","order":"05.13.007.3878"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/10.21"},"Ex. 10:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.3b","order":"05.13.007.3880"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.12"},"Rev. 6:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.4a","order":"05.13.007.3882"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/21.15"},"Luke 21:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.5a","order":"05.13.007.3884"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.1"},"D&C 58:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.6a","order":"05.13.007.3886"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/53.4"},"Isa. 53:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/27.26"},"Matt. 27:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.5.4-7"},"2 Ne. 9:5 (4–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.6b","order":"05.13.007.3888"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.7a","order":"05.13.007.3890"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/9.33"},"Rom. 9:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.8a","order":"05.13.007.3892"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.33.32-34"},"Rom. 8:33 (32–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.8b","order":"05.13.007.3894"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.4"},"Isa. 11:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.9a","order":"05.13.007.3896"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.31"},"Rom. 8:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.9b","order":"05.13.007.3898"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.26"},"Ps. 102:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.10a","order":"05.13.007.3900"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.38"},"D&C 1:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.10b","order":"05.13.007.3902"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-in-darkness"},"TG Walking in Darkness"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.11a","order":"05.13.007.3904"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/12.8"},"Deut. 12:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/17.6"},"Judg. 17:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.11b","order":"05.13.007.3906"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.70"},"D&C 133:70"],"."]]}
